      "span_text": "The physiological and metabolic tests used to characterize the strains included the ability to use different carbon substrates and energy sources, a variety of electron acceptors, fermentative growth (Table  l) , and growth tests at different temperature, pH and salinity; they have been described in a previous paper [CITATION_1] ."
